                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d709">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Leishman</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-02-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 28, 1903</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay inquires if Mr. Leishman has made renewed formal demand for an audience
                    with the Sultan as instructed in Mr. Hay’s telegram of February 25; and if so,
                    when?)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
